  "couplingIntensity": "Moderate",
  "description": "Ouroboros's strange attractor output feeds directly into Overdub's tape delay input — chaos is the source material. Whatever the attractor generates becomes what gets looped, warped, and echoed. AudioToFM coupling: ouro_attractorOutput → dub_delayInput, amount 0.55. Deterministic chaos enters the dub machine; what emerges from the spring reverb is a strange loop of the strange loop.",
